game.name: Pregnant Elsa Baby Birth
game.description:
The day has come your favorite Queen Elsa has been waiting for long. She was pregnant and the time has come when she is supposed to deliver a baby. You need to rush her to the hospital where she will get the right kind of treatment this time. Even her doctor said that she is ready to give birth to a baby today after reaching the hospital. Oh girls! She will have a cute boy and it is getting difficult for her to wait anymore. She needs a valuable helping hand today. Join Pregnant Elsa Baby Birth and get ready to provide her and her baby with the needful attention!

We hope that her boy will have her unmatched magical powers and the gorgeous eyes of his father. Call 191 and take care of her until ambulance arrives! Start this brand new doctor game with preparing the maternity bag that she will take along with her while rushing to the hospital! She is in her room now and you have taken a responsibility to collect all the items showed on the left side of the screen. Make sure to drag and drop a fluffily blanket, some cute baby clothes, some diapers and a suitable cap. Do not forget to collect the feeding bottle. 

Once it is done, get ready to take care of the job of a doctor in the hospital in this one of the best games for girls. Give her an injection to help her lessen the labor pain, and some extra oxygen, if required, to make her feel better! Go to the baby and take her to the cradle and help him go through a complete routine check up! Do not forget to undergo him some basic measurements to check if his health is ok. Put him to the right of his mother arms after making sure that everything is ok in this html5 princess surgery game!
